{code}
In 0.7 v.toString() returns following string:
{code:java}
{1:0.1,3:0.3}
{code}
but in 0.8 it returns
{code:java}
{1:0.1,3:0.3,}
{code}
As you can see, there is extra comma at the end of the string.

